name: L'Eagle Eagle
description: The L'Eagle Eagle hybrid is a blend of Candy Haze and Skunk #6 genetics offered at L'Eagle Services in Denver, Colorado. It’s fruity on the inhale, while the exhale brings a sweet and spicy aftertaste alongside an inspirational buzz that encourages activity. Highly potent and energetic, this is a great daytime strain for users with a high THC tolerance.
attributes_title: Happy, Energetic, Uplifted, Creative, Talkative, Depression, Fatigue, Stress, Inflammation, Headaches, Dry Mouth
